Florida rapper Aaron Waters Better know as Therealadot lildot , was originally born in Dover Delaware .With his Fathers absence and his mother‘s Mentorship and musical guidance this made a young Emcee thirst for the sport of Hip-Hop stepping on the scene in the late 80s early 90s in a forever evolving genre He was always listening writing, and challenging others to compete. With a brief stay and the United States army he was able to utilize networking skills and was able to fund his first studio back in 2009.  With a slew of music counting 200+ all recorded and engineered while in Iraq.  The father took a brief pause in the music, gathering bearings and enjoying new bundles of life.  Where he now lives in Florida sitting on a large catalog of timeless music. Classics such as Pen God 123 and four. “The Birthday Tape , Vibes of 2023 and more
